<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-7057] Issue with password having double &amp;&amp;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-7057</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;there is an issue with handling password with double &amp;amp;&amp;amp; even when wrapping it into RAW() constraint &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For instance the use of URI &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://hostname/script.php?authMethod=Basic&amp;amp;authPassword=RAW(pa&amp;amp;&amp;amp;word)&amp;amp;authUsername=usr&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://hostname/script.php?authMethod=Basic&amp;amp;authPassword=RAW(pa&amp;amp;&amp;amp;word)&amp;amp;authUsername=usr&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;throws the exception: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;org.apache.camel.ResolveEndpointFailedException: Failed to resolve endpoint: &lt;a href=&quot;http://hostname/script.php?authMethod=Basic&amp;amp;authPassword=RAW(pa&amp;amp;&amp;amp;word)&amp;amp;authUsername=usr&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://hostname/script.php?authMethod=Basic&amp;amp;authPassword=RAW(pa&amp;amp;&amp;amp;word)&amp;amp;authUsername=usr&lt;/a&gt; due to: Invalid uri syntax: Double &amp;amp;&amp;amp; marker found. Check the uri and remove the duplicate &amp;amp; marker. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
